 "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span></span><![endif]>Basic rating which determines how much raw
  firepower it takes to completely destroy the armor component.<span
  style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-ansi-la=
nguage:
  EN-GB'> </span></p>
